'''''Corulag''''' was a [[Bulk cruiser/Legends|bulk cruiser]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] during the early years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

Modified for assault, ''Corulag'' participated in the [[First Battle of Borleias]], where, serving as a platform of [[Defender Wing]], it launched the eight [[Gamma-class ATR-6 assault transport]]s that participated in the battle.

